data.description: Welcome to your dream home located on a picturesque pondview lot in a charming community. This meticulously crafted 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence boasts a versatile flex room, ideal for your personal needs, whether it be a home office, fitness area, or relaxation space. Step into the heart of the home and be greeted by a gourmet kitchen fit for a chef's delight. Adorned with luxurious quartz countertops, a double oven, and an upgraded faucet, this kitchen is sure to inspire culinary creativity. Embrace the efficiency and convenience of the all-natural gas community, while indulging in resort-style amenities that elevate everyday living. Unwind in the lavish primary suite featuring upgraded closet organizers for optimal storage and organization. The ensuite bathroom is adorned with modern fixtures and features a tankless water heater, ensuring comfort and efficiency. Experience seamless living with smart home technology that provides added convenience to your daily routine. Marvel at the architectural details including archway accents that add character and charm to the open concept living spaces. Step outside to the screened-in lanai, where you can enjoy the serene pond view and embrace the outdoor lifestyle in comfort and style. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite property your forever home. Schedule a showing today and embark on a journey to luxurious living!
